d.	Submit an explanation on why travel expenses such as meals, hotel accommodation, and travel allowances of municipal officials and employees during the Strategic Planning and Budgeting for Executive and Legislative Managers in the total amount of ₱399,300.00 were charged to 5% Calamity Fund and was held at Clark, Pampanga instead of conducting the planning within the Municipality of Mangaldan; 
e.	Instruct the Municipal Accountant to submit the required supporting documents to support the disbursements on traveling expenses to avoid the issuance of Notice of Suspension/Disallowance in audit; and 
